OL,6,FA doctor who sold ketamine to Friends
OL,7,Fstar Matthew Perry before he died
OL,8,Ffollowing an overdose is the first to
OL,9,Fbe jailed over the actor's death.
OL,11,FDr Salvador Plasencia, 44, was
OL,12,Fsentenced to two and a half years in
OL,13,Fprison on Wednesday after he admitted
OL,14,Fto illegally selling large amounts of
OL,15,Fketamine to Perry.
OL,17,FThe doctor, who was also handed two
OL,18,Fyears of probation, admitted to taking
OL,19,Fadvantage of the actor, knowing he was
OL,20,Fa struggling addict.
