OL,6,FThough he did not supply the dose that
OL,7,Fauthorities say killed the actor, the
OL,8,Fjudge said: "You and others helped Mr
OL,9,FPerry on the road to such an ending by
OL,10,Fcontinuing to feed his ketamine
OL,11,Faddiction."
OL,13,FHe added: "You exploited Mr Perry's
OL,14,Faddiction for your own profit."
OL,16,FPlasencia was the first to be
OL,17,Fsentenced of the five defendants who
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty in connection with
OL,19,FPerry's death at age 54 in 2023.
