OL,4,Cstar Matthew Perry jailed
OL,6,FPerry's mother and two half sisters
OL,7,Fgave tearful victim impact statements
OL,8,Fbefore the sentencing.
OL,10,F"The world mourns my brother,"
OL,11,FMadeleine Morrison said. "He was
OL,12,Feveryone's favourite friend."
OL,14,FPerry had been taking the surgical
OL,15,Fanaesthetic ketamine legally as a
OL,16,Ftreatment for depression. But when his
OL,17,Fregular doctor wouldn't provide it in
OL,18,Fthe amounts he wanted, he turned to
OL,19,FPlasencia, who admitted to illegally
OL,20,Fselling to Perry, knowing he was a
OL,21,Fstruggling addict.
