OL,11,FPlasencia's lawyers tried to give a
OL,12,Fsympathetic portrait of him as a man
OL,13,Fwho rose out of poverty to become a
OL,14,Fdoctor beloved by his patients, some
OL,15,Fof whom provided testimonials about
OL,16,Fhim for the court.
OL,18,FThe attorneys called his selling to
OL,19,FPerry "reckless" and "the biggest
OL,20,Fmistake of his life."
