OL,6,FPlasencia pleaded guilty in July to
OL,7,Ffour counts of distribution of
OL,8,Fketamine.
OL,10,FProsecutors agreed to drop five
OL,11,Fdifferent counts. The agreement came
OL,12,Fwith no sentencing guarantees, and
OL,13,Flegally, he could have been handed up
OL,14,Fto 40 years.
OL,16,FThe other four defendants who reached
OL,17,Fdeals to plead guilty will be
OL,18,Fsentenced at their own hearings in the
OL,19,Fcoming months.
