OL,7,Fyears, dating back to his time on
OL,8,FFriends, when he became one of the
OL,9,Fbiggest stars of his generation as
OL,10,FChandler Bing.
OL,12,FHe starred alongside Jennifer Aniston,
OL,13,FCourteney Cox, Lisa Kudrow, Matt
OL,14,FLeBlanc and David Schwimmer for ten
OL,15,Fseasons from 1994 to 2004 on NBC's
OL,16,Fmegahit.
